{"tid":260001,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（噴血）「童貞殺」毛衣再進化！","createTime":"2017-05-27T11:35:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-28T02:30:30.000Z","uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c9b1de406a41ac5e36d08247c6b7b955477e7f8f","tid":260001,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T11:35:32.000Z","msg":"「童貞殺」的原版只是露背毛衣，大露背的設計展現美背、側乳和水蛇腰，S曲線讓人受不了，甚至還有人將衣服反穿，胸前重點部位僅用緞帶遮掩，也難怪網友將其封為「能殺死處男的『童貞殺』毛衣」。(更多新聞就在中天必POTV)<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/27/193513_62e74725da8b9cb4977a443763832f26.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F27%2F193513_62e74725da8b9cb4977a443763832f26.jpg&h=7f39b380&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/27/193517_62e74725da8b9cb4977a443763832f26.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F27%2F193517_62e74725da8b9cb4977a443763832f26.jpg&h=6985fd86&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/27/193524_63945f36a763009973626471158e7557.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F27%2F193524_63945f36a763009973626471158e7557.jpg&h=28ddaa65&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a333bd21bc88888805cbacd95c95ed971581fbd4","tid":260001,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T11:36:51.000Z","msg":"號稱能夠殺死處男的「童貞殺」毛衣，已被許多女神、男人或是偽娘穿過，從日本紅到台灣的超殺毛衣，最近又推出進化版，原本只是露背和露股溝，如今進化成正面、側面都殺出重圍，放肆展露。<br />\n<br />\n進化版童真殺在日本《amazon》已經開始販售，要價2430日圓（約664元台幣），照片可見，衣服乳溝處開大口，側邊大挖空，從側乳、腰部到大腿根部都能一覽無遺，更別說幾乎裸空的背部。<br />\n<a href=\"http://bepo.ctitv.com.tw/2017/05/220864/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbepo.ctitv.com.tw%2F2017%2F05%2F220864%2F&d=JztM1fgw8aysWUEKtbiZ6gRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=b09dbb56\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bepo.ctitv.com.tw/2017/05/220864/</a>"},{"pid":"e0f0f6b9a10af4e486d842d7aca1258138198d10","tid":260001,"uid":11798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T11:38:59.000Z","msg":"港女能否一戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4b9d3d345c0a56ce407af1c98fc73185fd1d1d2","tid":260001,"uid":79481,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T11:42:43.000Z","msg":"無第一代咁靚<br />\n<br />\n呢件太曝露 無乜美感"},{"pid":"4967315b1fa975c6b8266317d49c4256e34c94ea","tid":260001,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T15:02:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/27/230142_a9120818f2c5d139e9efabfc50614d13.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F27%2F230142_a9120818f2c5d139e9efabfc50614d13.jpg&h=54c37090&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/27/230157_2647d85660b8f68dc79e254fcfec171e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F27%2F230157_2647d85660b8f68dc79e254fcfec171e.jpg&h=d09a7d9e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"392a23369d6720c3b171ad045f984c0523654fde","tid":260001,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T15:05:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/27/230530_2985d2bb938a49454ebbfc3410a00e39.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F27%2F230530_2985d2bb938a49454ebbfc3410a00e39.jpg&h=520f941d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb5796a23afa6d210f54a43614f0f4c9e6fa32f4","tid":260001,"uid":13149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T15:07:07.0